    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with its signature 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and the factory-spec GKN variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including a comprehensive Vanos system overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension remains tight, utilizing MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup with refreshed bushings. While the finish shows honest patina from spirited road use, the powertrain exhibits linear power delivery and the cooling system has been updated with an aluminum radiator to manage thermal loads during high-performance driving. A true analog masterpiece ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
